{"tid":280774,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"42碎老女人林志玲薄紗挺進撒哈拉 受封「沙漠最美」","createTime":"2017-06-12T09:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T09:14:29.000Z","uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d588753c4778d980cee21bbd657b5fbd2130f53b","tid":280774,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:50:46.000Z","msg":"42碎老女人林志玲薄紗挺進撒哈拉 受封「沙漠最美」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/06/10/phponhMP2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2FphponhMP2.jpg&h=6f3228b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林志玲赴撒哈拉沙漠出外景。（翻攝自微博）<br />\n〔娛樂頻道／綜合報導〕42碎老女人林志玲日前為真人秀節目赴摩洛哥出外景，她身穿薄紗在沙漠中騎駱駝，唯美模樣，被讚是「沙漠最美畫面」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/06/10/php90PEMq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2Fphp90PEMq.jpg&h=68f4c38f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林志玲騎駱駝的畫面，被讚是「沙漠最美」。（翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/06/10/phpzXeZVo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2FphpzXeZVo.jpg&h=8ed1e692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n42碎老女人林志玲在沙漠拍攝許多唯美照。（翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n42碎老女人林志玲在微博曬出多張花絮照，她一邊哼唱著蘇運瑩的《野子》，一邊前進撒哈拉沙漠，為了防阻風沙，特地在頭、肩披上薄紗絲巾，增添幾分神祕感，除了甜美自拍，還對鏡頭擺出搞怪姿勢，難得到沙漠出外景，讓她大讚：「見到了這一輩子無與倫比最寧靜的美麗星空！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/06/10/phpHtYKMg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2FphpHtYKMg.jpg&h=e3a3dc9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林志玲在沙漠中開心自拍。（翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/06/10/phpHB5xuF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2FphpHB5xuF.jpg&h=618872b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林志玲騎駱駝的畫面，被讚是「沙漠最美」。（翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/06/10/phpyDIG8R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2FphpyDIG8R.jpg&h=eeb621f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林志玲赴撒哈拉沙漠出外景。（翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/06/10/phpSVejri.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2FphpSVejri.jpg&h=228a2c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林志玲曬出多張錄影花絮照。（翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n轉貼自: <a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2095464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2095464&d=rGbzPBv%2FvAtRghWU3Hqj%2BQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=4ebc5c4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2095464&h=2774f636\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2095464</a>"},{"pid":"b63127acd22ee21c16e8b9a996283e6c1090c665","tid":280774,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:03:26.000Z","msg":"女熱大陸新片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bcea014e615e55c022ac1327602240e627faa8","tid":280774,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T14:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c658cc47bb921cbef24b7b8820a27508264dc79b","tid":280774,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:30:22.000Z","msg":"一帶一露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac